                <li><strong>Prepare the Home for Recovery:</strong> Help get the home ready for their return after surgery. This might include deep cleaning, doing laundry, preparing and freezing some simple, low-salt meals, and setting up a comfortable, accessible recovery space on the main floor with everything they might need within reach.</li>
