                <li><strong>Monitoring and Reporting:</strong> You are the first line of defense. Help by tracking vital signs like temperature, blood pressure, and daily weight. Keep a simple log of these numbers and any new symptoms (like pain, nausea, or swelling) to report to the transplant team during check-in calls or at appointments.</li>
